doc.title: Iisetingi zehlabathi

example.domain: Unokongeza igama lesizinda, njenge {{url}}, ukungabandakanyi lonke igama lesizinda.
example.url: Ungakhuphela ngaphandle amakhonkco athile ngokudibanisa ikhonkco, elifana {{url}}.
example.glob: Ungongeza i {{glob}} ipateni, efana {{minimatch}}, ukwenzela uthelekiso oludidayo.

doc.script: Ungasebenzisa kwakhona izikripthi zejs ukufumana ulawulo oluntsonkothileyo.
doc.checkedUseScript: Nokuba uyawenza na owakho umbhalo, qaphela ukuba kufuneka ukhangele zombini iibhokisi ngexesha elinye ukwenza umbhalo usebenze.

example1.commentTitle: Ngoku kwiwebhusayithi ye-{{youtube}}, kufuneka uvule i-{{youtube}}'s {{watch}} okanye i-{{shorts}} iphepha kwi-tab entsha.
example1.page: : Umahluko yinto ye-URL yephepha lewebhu langoku Ngeenkcukacha, Nceda ubone
example1.minimatch: : {{glob}} indlela yokudibanisa, usebenzisa i {{minimatch}} ilayibrari, indlela yokusebenzisa Nceda Bona, okanye unokukhangela indlela yokusebenzisa {{glob}}.
example1.wholeCode: Intsingiselo yekhowudi yonke kukuba ngoku kwi-YouTube {{www}} igama lesizinda, ukuba ikhonkco elicofaziweyo ligama lesizinda esifanayo kwaye indlela iqala ngo {{watch}} okanye {{shorts}}, emva koko ithebhu entsha iphepha ekunene lizakuba Vula.
